description:
NRFreqRelation: Table storing NR frequency relation parameters for cell reselection.

dateTime: Timestamp indicating when the data was recorded.
Area_Name: Geographic area where the cell is located.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell (gNB/gNodeB).
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  Unique identifier of the serving cell.
Id4:  Unique identifier of the frequency relation.
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
NRFreqRelation.tReselectionNR: Time to reselection for NR.
NRFreqRelation.tReselectionNrSfMedium: Time to reselection for NR, medium scenario.
NRFreqRelation.ueMCNrFreqRelProfileRef: Reference to UE-specific multi-connectivity NR frequency relation profile.
NRFreqRelation.threshXLowP: Lower threshold for X-axis parameter P.
NRFreqRelation.threshXLowQ: Lower threshold for X-axis parameter Q.
NRFreqRelation.plmnIdList: List of PLMN IDs.
NRFreqRelation.sIntraSearchQ: Intra-frequency search parameters for Q.
NRFreqRelation.anrMeasOn: Flag indicating whether A-NR measurements are enabled.
NRFreqRelation.mcpcPSCellNrFreqRelProfileRef: Reference to MCPC secondary cell NR frequency relation profile.
NRFreqRelation.sIntraSearchP: Intra-frequency search parameters for P.
NRFreqRelation.cellReselectionSubPriority: Sub-priority for cell reselection.
NRFreqRelation.qRxLevMin: Minimum received quality level (RxLev).
NRFreqRelation.cellReselectionPriority: Priority for cell reselection.
NRFreqRelation.qOffsetFreq: Frequency offset.
NRFreqRelation.pMax: Maximum value for parameter P.
NRFreqRelation.tReselectionNrSfHigh: Time to reselection for NR, high scenario.
NRFreqRelation.plmnRestriction: Flag indicating whether PLMN restriction is enabled.
NRFreqRelation.nRFrequencyRef: Reference to NR frequency.
NRFreqRelation.intraFreqMCFreqRelProfileRef: Reference to intra-frequency multi-connectivity frequency relation profile.
NRFreqRelation.mdtMeasOn: Flag indicating whether MDT measurements are enabled.
NRFreqRelation.threshXHighQ: Higher threshold for X-axis parameter Q.
NRFreqRelation.threshXHighP: Higher threshold for X-axis parameter P.
NRFreqRelation.trStSaNrFreqRelProfileRef: Reference to TR-ST SA NR frequency relation profile.
NRFreqRelation.reservedBy: Information on the entity reserving this entry.
NRFreqRelation.nRFreqRelationId:  Unique identifier of the NR frequency relation.
NRFreqRelation.mcpcPCellNrFreqRelProfileRef: Reference to MCPC primary cell NR frequency relation profile.
NRFreqRelation.qQualMin: Minimum quality value.
